Even more ruthless than Yama

12
00:00:24.933 --> 00:00:28.800
Think about it, if the emperor passes the throne to Yama

13
00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:31.100
Wouldn't he be more at ease?

14
00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:36.966
If I were to execute two people today

15
00:00:37.733 --> 00:00:39.866
The death must be

16
00:00:41.100 --> 00:00:41.900
Demon

17
00:00:45.566 --> 00:00:46.900
Lucky to have you

18
00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:49.766
Otherwise, the consequences will be unimaginable

19
00:00:56.800 --> 00:00:59.500
So dangerous, so dangerous

20
00:00:59.733 --> 00:01:02.433
I didn't expect that Wang Xun would let me go

21
00:01:02.533 --> 00:01:04.200
