26
00:01:12.133 --> 00:01:13.633
Father let me go

27
00:01:13.800 --> 00:01:16.466
Why? Because you're cruel

28
00:01:16.700 --> 00:01:20.000
For the sake of ascendancy, even the emperor's life can be sacrificed

29
00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.300
In the eyes of the emperor

30
00:01:21.300 --> 00:01:22.000
See

31
00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:25.300
