32
00:01:25.300 --> 00:01:26.466
So?

33
00:01:27.066 --> 00:01:29.700
Father has agreed that I will inherit the throne

34
00:01:29.733 --> 00:01:31.266
As it should be

35
00:01:31.266 --> 00:01:33.400
So I didn't punish you.

36
00:01:33.400 --> 00:01:37.000
So as not to overcome the stain for you in the future

37
00:01:37.300 --> 00:01:39.600
But don't be too happy, Prince

38
00:01:39.733 --> 00:01:41.866
Wang Xu is scheming

39
00:01:41.866 --> 00:01:43.400
If you make him a prince

40
00:01:43.400 --> 00:01:45.466
It will be a scourge in the future

41
00:01:45.500 --> 00:01:48.266
So we have to root as soon as possible

42
00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:53.033
I'll ask him if he can't see the sun tomorrow.

